{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Step aboard the MS Estonia which tragically sank on the 28th of September 1994 in the Baltic Sea.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>The Experience</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on the final voyage of the ill-fated MS Estonia and experience the final moments of the ships tragic demise. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As a passenger, you get to explore the ship in an immersive simulation that accurately depicts the ships final moments.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Facing an intense storm and critical system failure, the MS Estonia's life-boat system becomes inoperable, and you must find another way to safety before time runs out or stay aboard.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The MS Estonia has never been recreated to this level of detail. The entire exterior of the ship is explorable, with the bridge also being accessible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Background of the MS Estonia</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The MS Estonia, a tragic chapter in maritime history, was a passenger ferry that sank in the Baltic Sea on September 28, 1994. Departing from Tallinn, Estonia, en route to Stockholm, Sweden, the vessel met its end in a violent storm. The disaster claimed the lives of over 800 passengers and crew, making it one of the worst maritime tragedies of the 20th century.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Note: This is a simulation experience not a story-based game</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1733537771","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848550/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1733537771","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2848550/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1733537771","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com